      <title>拜登升级与日本的防务关系旨在对抗中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-upgrades-defense-ties-with-japan-aimed-at-countering-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统拜登接待日本首相岸田文雄进行正式访问，美国和日本公布了深化安全关系的计划，这显示了日本作为对抗中国的关键盟友的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-upgrades-defense-ties-with-japan-aimed-at-countering-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 02:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称中国没有理由对与盟友的演习“反应过度”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-says-no-reason-for-china-to-overreact-to-drills-with-allies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位白宫顾问表示，中国没有理由对美国、日本、澳大利亚和菲律宾在有争议的南中国海的联合海上巡逻“反应过度”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-says-no-reason-for-china-to-overreact-to-drills-with-allies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 01:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默和坎特威尔为美国 TikTok 禁令的前进之路而奋斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/schumer-cantwell-struggle-on-path-forward-for-us-tiktok-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国禁止流行的 TikTok 应用程序的立法在参议院仍陷入僵局，周三关键的民主党人在参议院难以达成共识。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/schumer-cantwell-struggle-on-path-forward-for-us-tiktok-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁收购美国钢铁公司的竞标受到延长反垄断审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/nippon-steel-bid-to-buy-us-steel-gets-extended-antitrust-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三名知情人士透露，美国司法部已对新日铁以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的收购案展开了广泛的反垄断调查，这为完成交易设置了额外的法律障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/nippon-steel-bid-to-buy-us-steel-gets-extended-antitrust-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部审查私募股权并购披露</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/justice-department-scrutinizing-private-equity-merger-disclosure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员周三表示，司法部正在调查一些私募股权公司是否可能在之前的合并中故意隐瞒信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/justice-department-scrutinizing-private-equity-merger-disclosure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:24:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴蒙、库克、贝索斯出席拜登为日本岸田先生举行的国宴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/dimon-cook-bezos-attend-biden-state-dinner-for-japan-s-kishida</link>
      <description><![CDATA[领先的技术、金融和媒体高管周三齐聚白宫，参加向日本首相岸田文雄举行的国宴，美国总统乔·拜登希望通过这场众星云集的庆祝活动来加强这两个盟友之间的安全和经济关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/dimon-cook-bezos-attend-biden-state-dinner-for-japan-s-kishida</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多否认中国干预试图帮助他的选举的说法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/trudeau-rejects-claim-china-meddled-to-try-to-help-his-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多在一次公开调查中表示，鉴于两国之间的高度紧张关系，他发现中国政府“非常不可能”希望他的自由党赢得最近的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/trudeau-rejects-claim-china-meddled-to-try-to-help-his-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 21:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
